---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About · NilaTales"
  description="About NilaTales — moon-tales for Tamil children."
  lang="en"
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 prose-ta">
    <h1 lang="ta" class="text-4xl font-display font-bold text-nila-950 mb-2">நிலா கதைகள் பற்றி</h1>
    <p lang="en" class="text-slate-500 font-display italic mb-8">About NilaTales</p>

    <p lang="ta" class="text-lg text-nila-900 leading-relaxed">
      <strong>நிலா</strong> என்றால் நிலவு. <strong>கதை</strong> என்றால் சொல்லப்படும் செய்தி.
      நிலா கதைகள் என்பது நிலவொளியில் சொல்லப்படும் கதைகள் — தூக்க நேரத்திற்கு
      முன், விளக்கு ஒளியில், அம்மா அப்பா பாட்டி தாத்தா சொல்லும் கதைகள்.
    </p>

    <p lang="en" class="text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
      <em>Nila</em> means moon. <em>Katai</em> means story. NilaTales is stories told under
      moonlight — bedtime stories from amma, appa, paatti, and thatha.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-6 text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      NilaTales is a quiet place for Tamil-speaking children (ages 6–12) and the grown-ups who read
      with them. We tell three kinds of stories:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside text-slate-700">
      <li><strong>திருக்குறள் கதைகள்</strong> — Valluvar's 1330 couplets, one short story at a time.</li>
      <li><strong>பஞ்சதந்திர கதைகள்</strong> — the classic animal fables from the five tantras.</li>
      <li><strong>கதைகள்</strong> — original moral tales and regional folktales.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Plus comics, lullabies, and printable activities so every story can be touched, drawn, and
      re-read at bedtime.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-nila-950 mt-12 mb-3">A sister site of NitviTalks</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      NilaTales is a sister site of
      <a href="https://nitvi.kingspath.in" class="text-nila-700 underline hover:text-nila-900">NitviTalks</a>,
      where a 10-year-old teaches electronics, coding, robotics, AI, and English through short
      videos. Both sites are part of the
      <a href="https://kingspath.in" class="text-nila-700 underline hover:text-nila-900">Kingspath</a>
      family of learning projects.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-nila-950 mt-12 mb-3">Open source</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      NilaTales is open source on
      <a href="https://github.com/nivinlabs/nilatales" class="text-nila-700 underline hover:text-nila-900">
        GitHub
      </a>.
      Tamil font: <strong>Noto Serif Tamil</strong>. Built with Astro.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
